# arvo-hash

L2 hash-domain types and algorithm contracts. ContentHash aliases
arvo-bits Bits<28> for call-site domain naming. Generic streaming
Hasher<const N: u8> trait with blanket HasherExt<const N: u8> for
oneshot ergonomics lets downstream code parameterise over algorithm
choice; concrete algorithms (FNV, xxHash, CRC32) ship in follow-up
rounds as trait implementors. `#![no_std]`, no alloc.
